					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Go ahead and mess with T, it's basically the 'Horizontal reset' thingy for each scanline, and the 'Vertical Reset' thingy for the top.
<br />
<br />The PPU doesn't mess with T in the middle of the frame anyway, it just reads some bits from it every scanline to reset the horizontal scroll.</div>

					
