					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Well then I can't answer you because pretty much all I know was put into the document.
<br />
<br />I don't think I said anything wrong about that cycle 256 thing, but maybe different source numbered the cycles differently ?
<br />
<br />Anyway, on your second $2006 write, it should land either always before cycle 256 or always after - by always I mean in all cases of jitter. If you fall between the two (so that, depending on jitter condition, you will write after or before 256) you will get shaking graphics, because in some cases the V scroll will be incremented before your write, and sometimes after.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Life is complex: it has both real and imaginary components.</div>
					<br clear="all" /><br />

